{"tid":2328321,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"男優最愛哪位AV女星　「金手指」加藤鷹回答太驚人！","createTime":"2020-12-16T13:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T14:11:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e74bebee47f13816618b9ef88bfc7aa59d4258","tid":2328321,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"說起日本AV，大家而熟能詳的肯定是女優，而出演AV的，不光是女優還得有男優的賣力演出，才有最後的作品，但是男優去少有成名的，國內的AV達人一劍浣春秋在談及日本暗黑界藝能圈時，提到每次訪問AV男優「最喜歡的女優時，總是得到讓人不太滿意的答案」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/12/27/2325767-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F12%2F27%2F2325767-PH.jpg&h=059ade67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲加藤鷹喜歡的女優是過去的人氣女優。 （圖／翻攝自加藤鷹微博）<br />\n<br />\n一劍浣春秋表示「像加藤鷹會說他最喜歡「豊丸」，我的天啊，雖然也是名噪一時喊水會結凍的女優，但她今年已經53歲搞不好做阿嬤了，你要讀者有共鳴實在不容易；トニー大木(東尼大木)比較精，他會告訴你最喜歡波多野結衣，這是因為他之前常跑台灣做活動已經是老油條了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/28/2579717-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F28%2F2579717-PH.jpg&h=fd03ddb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲有「暗黑周董」的AV男優東尼大木，記不得女優姓名。（圖／翻攝自東尼大木推特）<br />\n<br />\n原來不是男優怕得罪人，真正的原因是男優們根本不記得自己和誰拍過片了，所以每當有人問「你最喜歡誰」，男優們大多會回答你的是讓他們印象最深刻的女優，而會讓他們印象比較深刻的女優，大多都是生涯初期合作的對象。加上AV界有著男女優不能私下見面或聯絡的不成文規定，男優年紀一大幾乎都是拍完就忘，一劍浣春秋就說，トニー大木(東尼大木)更扯，你拿才剛發行的片子(就大概三四個月前拍攝的作品)問他女優叫什麼名字，他記不得是正常的，搞不好還會問你：「我有和她合作過嗎？」。"},{"pid":"9c7309d43494e1c72d6f5cfd885efa44003caec4","tid":2328321,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"屌到唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8500b0c2105f5417ddd7670d4b9e6fb2a057083c","tid":2328321,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"施巴呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd51b0ea58d846ae5ef23cb4637e8d36b165844","tid":2328321,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8500b0c2105f5417ddd7670d4b9e6fb2a057083c","tid":2328321,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"施巴呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"多到唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dd00a60b7b15653657dd2df520d748530607ad","tid":2328321,"uid":306689,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"其實即係問皇帝同邊個宫女瞓過一樣。"},{"pid":"0f8017a076ea05feadd85688bba6333874bc950b","tid":2328321,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c7309d43494e1c72d6f5cfd885efa44003caec4","tid":2328321,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"屌到唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:09:08.000Z","msg":"我睇完一晚都唔記得d名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1454466b75aa7f304466f053925f24a0fb626394","tid":2328321,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c7309d43494e1c72d6f5cfd885efa44003caec4","tid":2328321,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:01:31.000Z","msg":"屌到唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"你問我我都唔記得晒咁多個啦，何況佢哋"},{"pid":"332b24bafbf0977111294ebd4a5d46